        {
            "utteranceID": "U10",
            "turnID": "T06",
            "participantID": "P02",
            "date": "2020-07-31",
            "time": "02:38:00",
            "utterance": "적도지방의 먹거리가 풍족한것처럼"
        },
        {
            "utteranceID": "U11",
            "turnID": "T07",
            "participantID": "P01",
            "date": "2020-07-31",
            "time": "02:38:00",
            "utterance": "아"
